EPN, Thu Oct 20 10:57:06 2016

List of files to update when doing a release (in a release branch or a
hotfix branch). These files have one or more of a version number,
date, or copyright information. Copyright information may not need to
be updated, but version number and date always need to be updated.

Files to update:
LICENSE     (version, date and copyright)
README      (version, date ***AND*** Easel tag in instructions)
scripts/*pl (version and date)
